                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>innocentissimo <lb n="3"/>et dulcissimo filio <lb n="4"/>Iulio Dafnidio qui vi<lb break="no" n="5"/>xit in s<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>eculo</abbr></expan> mensi<lb break="no" n="6"/>um quinque <lb n="7"/>onofito <note>sic</note> Laurentius <lb n="8"/>et Maximilla paren<lb break="no" n="9"/>tes contra vo<lb break="no" n="10"/>tum posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 7: onofito statt neofito.</p>
